# Creates a deterministic Link's House savestate from the ALTTP boot/name flow.
#
# Format:
#   frame_start..frame_end BUTTON[,BUTTON]
#
# The timing is calibrated against bsnes-mercury performance and the current
# AP_78856210104802680998 ALTTP patch used by the Beta-3 heartbeat proof.
1850..1870 START
1900..1920 A
1950..1970 START
